    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR1h0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T05:52:54.375+09:00">Mencius ait:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T05:53:01.223+09:00">"Homo quo differt a bestiis,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T05:53:09.381+09:00">minimum est.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T05:53:16.098+09:00"> Vulgares homines abjiciant illud ;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T05:53:22.243+09:00">sapiens vir servat illud.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T05:53:34.274+09:00">Chouenn clare intelligebaL (quid faciendum esset) in omnibus rebus curandis;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T05:54:45.862+09:00">clare dispiciebat (quid agere deceret) in hominum mutuis officiis implendis.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T05:55:18.263+09:00">Obsequens humanitati et aequitati agebat;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-23a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T05:55:57.373+09:00">non magno labore insistebat viae humanitatis et aequitatis.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-19a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-20T00:47:11.118+09:00">Meng Tseu ait:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-19a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-20T00:47:21.573+09:00">“Ne agas quid ipse (naturali aequitatissensu cognoscis) non esse agendum,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-19a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-20T00:47:31.184+09:00">ne cupias quod ipse (naturali aequitatissensu cognoscis) non esse optandum.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-20a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-20T00:47:31.596+09:00"> Ita si facias, jam satis erit”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-4a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-02T21:54:36.16+09:00">Meng tseu dixit:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-4a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-02T21:55:44.439+09:00">Universae res simut paesto sunt in nobis, i. e. natura humanae menti indidit principia ex quibus rerum omnium rationes cognosci possunt.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-4a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-02T21:56:39.956+09:00">Si quis mentis oculos convertens in seimpsum, videat se esse perfectum,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-4a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-02T21:56:46.445+09:00">gaudium nullum majus est.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-4a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-02T21:58:16.444+09:00">Si quis conetur diligere alios sicut seipsum et ewta agere, quaesita perfectione nihil propius erit.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-02T22:00:45.618+09:00">Meng tseu dixit:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-02T22:05:17.043+09:00">"Res quas quum quaerimus, invenimus,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-02T22:05:58.59+09:00">et quum negligiimus, amittimus,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-02T22:01:47.185+09:00">tung quaerere utile est ad inveniendas eas.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-02T22:06:31.593+09:00">Eae sunt res quas quaerimus in nobis, nempe virtuetes in nobis ingenitae, quae sunt humanitas, aequitas, urbanitas, prudentia.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-02T22:03:18.81+09:00">Res ad quas quaerendas sunt servandae regulae,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-3a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-02T22:03:39.177+09:00">et ad quas obtinendas est, i.e. requiritur, coeleste decretum,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-3a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-02T22:04:18.949+09:00">tunc quaerere non utile est ad obtinendas eas.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-4a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-02T22:05:03.87+09:00">Eae sunt res quas quaerimus extra nos, nempe, divitiae, honores, ..."</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
